# App Structure and Routing

## Expo Router File Structure

The app uses Expo Router with file-based routing. Each directory represents a route group or screen.

### Main Routes
- [app/index.tsx](mdc:app/index.tsx) - Root redirect logic (signed in → session, signed out → sign-in)
- [app/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/_layout.tsx) - Root layout with providers ( Toast, Portal, ActionSheet)

### Chat Routes
- [app/(chat)/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/_layout.tsx) - Chat layout with bottom tabs
- [app/(chat)/session/index.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/session/index.tsx) - Session list screen
- [app/(chat)/session/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/session/_layout.tsx) - Session layout
- [app/(chat)/chat/index.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/chat/index.tsx) - Main chat interface
- [app/(chat)/chat/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/chat/_layout.tsx) - Chat layout
- [app/(chat)/detail/index.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/detail/index.tsx) - Chat detail view
- [app/(chat)/detail/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(chat)/detail/_layout.tsx) - Detail layout

### Settings Routes
- [app/(setting)/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(setting)/_layout.tsx) - Settings layout
- [app/(setting)/setting/index.tsx](mdc:app/(setting)/setting/index.tsx) - Settings screen
- [app/(setting)/setting/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/(setting)/setting/_layout.tsx) - Settings layout
- [app/(setting)/setting/provider.tsx](mdc:app/(setting)/setting/provider.tsx) - Settings provider

### Playground Routes
- [app/playground/_layout.tsx](mdc:app/playground/_layout.tsx) - Playground layout
- [app/playground/index.tsx](mdc:app/playground/index.tsx) - Component playground
- [app/playground/highlighter.tsx](mdc:app/playground/highlighter.tsx) - Code highlighting demo
- [app/playground/markdown.tsx](mdc:app/playground/markdown.tsx) - Markdown rendering demo
- [app/playground/toast.tsx](mdc:app/playground/toast.tsx) - Toast notifications demo
- [app/playground/tooltip.tsx](mdc:app/playground/tooltip.tsx) - Tooltip component demo

## Route Groups
- `(chat)` - Main chat functionality
- `(setting)` - App settings and configuration
- `playground` - Component development and testing

## Navigation Patterns
- Use `Redirect` component for programmatic navigation
- Use bottom tabs for main navigation in chat section
